
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-mip4-faerr-02.txt'>
    <title>"Foreign Agent Error Extension for Mobile IPv4", Charles Perkins</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-mip4-faerr-02.txt</link>
    <description>This document specifies a new extension for use by Foreign Agents operating Mobile IP for IPv4. Currently, a foreign agent cannot supply status information without destroying the ability for a mobile node to verify authentication data supplied by the home agent. The new extension solves this problem by making a better place for the foreign agent to provide its status information to the mobile node.</description>
    <dc:date>2005-09-21T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
